prompts.frontCover:
A full-body, 2D watercolor illustration of a young Asian couple, Lao Lao and Jordan, based on the reference photo. Lao Lao is a young woman with long, straight dark brown hair, wearing thin-rimmed round glasses, a light blue crewneck sweatshirt (logo omitted), and black pants. Jordan is a young man with short, dark, textured hair, wearing a tan hoodie and dark maroon sweatpants. In a humorous and lighthearted scene, Jordan is enthusiastically lifting Lao Lao off the ground in a big birthday hug, both with huge, joyful smiles. Lao Lao's legs are kicking playfully in the air. The background is a simplified, soft-focus watercolor wash of a cloudy sky over a calm body of water, hinting at the location in the photo but keeping the focus on the couple. The overall style is charming and artistic, with visible paper texture, soft color bleeds, and delicate brushstrokes.

Centered in the middle of the card, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my favorite human bean!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
